		</font></code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">In an action under this Act the burden of proving an
exemption under paragraph (d) of Section 3 is on the person claiming the exemption.</font></code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">
		</font></code><br><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">(Source: P.A. 85-1384.)</font></code><code><font size="2" face="Courier New">
